pageContext.claim: “Who is a worse governor, @BrianKempGA of Georgia or @dougducey of Arizona??? These are two RINO Republicans who fought against me and the Republican Party harder than any Democrat. They allowed states that I won easily to be stolen. Never forget, vote them out of office!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump lost both Georgia and Arizona by narrow margins, but his claims of fraud were never proven in court and the votes were certified.
